  "notes": [
    "Pinned OCI SDK contract: AnalyticsInstance lifecycle exposes CREATING, ACTIVE, UPDATING, DELETING, FAILED, INACTIVE, and DELETED. Repo-authored controller success is ACTIVE or INACTIVE, requeue covers CREATING and UPDATING, FAILED is terminal without requeue, and delete confirmation follows DELETING to DELETED or NotFound.",
